    for navbar.jsx




    Navbar Component

This is a responsive navigation bar built with React and Tailwind CSS. It works on both desktop and mobile.

Features

Logo: Clickable, links to home page.

Navigation Links: Home, All Food, Contact.

Search Bar:

Visible on desktop and mobile.

Has a search icon and placeholder text.

Cart Icon: Shows number of items.

User Section:

Shows Login button if not logged in.

Shows profile icon if logged in.

Mobile menu shows Logout button if logged in.

Mobile Menu:

Hidden by default, opens with hamburger button.

Contains search bar, links, and login/logout button.

Responsive Design: Layout adjusts for small and large screens.

Hover Effects: Smooth color and scale transitions on links and buttons.

How it works    
Uses state open to toggle mobile menu.

Uses context user to check login status.

Desktop menu visible on larger screens, mobile menu visible when opened.

Navigation uses NavLink from React Router.